name: 420 Cafe
description:
Panama is legalizing medicinal cannabis. If you buy this you are going to support me opening my coffeeshop and your local community nft art expo for Panamenians with the sweet new nft displays.

If you show me this token when you come to my coffeeshop you will get 1 free coffee from the best coffee grains in the world grown here in the valley of a province called Chiriqui, Panama and also a limited edition coffee cup designed by me.
